{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/nextjs/시작하기/nextjs공통템플릿적용하기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"GPT 하수인의 개발자 이야기"}},"mdx":{"id":"5c1a4677-d48e-5331-a7a7-9f33719be23a","excerpt":"","body":"\r\n<section>\r\n    <h3>nextjs는 router로 페이지를 설정하지 않던데, 그럼 공통적인 css 설정은 어디서 해야 하나요? navigation처럼 모든 페이지에 공통적으로 들어가는 컴포넌트는 어떻게 처리해야 하나요?</h3>\r\n\r\n    <p>pages 폴더 내 '_app.tsx' 파일의 내용을 수정하면 된다. Component는 각 페이지에서 렌더링되는 컴포넌트를 의미하고, 공통적으로 적용할 내용들을 해당 파일에서 작성하면 된다.</p>\r\n\r\n    <Highlighter code='/pages/_app.tsx\r\n    \r\n    import `@/styles/globals.css`\r\n    import type { AppProps } from `next/app`\r\n\r\n    export default function App({ Component, pageProps }: AppProps) {\r\n        return (<div>\r\n                <div>이 문구는 모든 페이지에서 보이게 됩니다.</div>\r\n                <Component {...pageProps} />\r\n        </div>);\r\n    }\r\n    '></Highlighter>\r\n\r\n    <Codesandbox url='https://codesandbox.io/p/github/ka0824/nextjs_prac/main?layout=%257B%2522sidebarPanel%2522%253A%2522EXPLORER%2522%252C%2522rootPanelGroup%2522%253A%257B%2522direction%2522%253A%2522horizontal%2522%252C%2522type%2522%253A%2522PANEL_GROUP%2522%252C%2522id%2522%253A%2522ROOT_LAYOUT%2522%252C%2522panels%2522%253A%255B%257B%2522type%2522%253A%2522PANEL_GROUP%2522%252C%2522direction%2522%253A%2522vertical%2522%252C%2522id%2522%253A%2522EDITOR%2522%252C%2522panels%2522%253A%255B%257B%2522type%2522%253A%2522PANEL%2522%252C%2522panelType%2522%253A%2522TABS%2522%252C%2522id%2522%253A%2522clhrnfw0e000a356nbitaxa0y%2522%257D%255D%252C%2522sizes%2522%253A%255B100%255D%257D%252C%257B%2522type%2522%253A%2522PANEL_GROUP%2522%252C%2522direction%2522%253A%2522vertical%2522%252C%2522id%2522%253A%2522DEVTOOLS%2522%252C%2522panels%2522%253A%255B%257B%2522type%2522%253A%2522PANEL%2522%252C%2522panelType%2522%253A%2522TABS%2522%252C%2522id%2522%253A%2522clhrnfw0e000c356niy96rh44%2522%257D%255D%252C%2522sizes%2522%253A%255B100%255D%257D%255D%252C%2522sizes%2522%253A%255B